==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Governess
<hw>Gov"ern*ess</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>governeresse</ets>. See <er>Governor</er>.]</ety> <def>A female
governor; a woman invested with authority to control and direct;
especially, one intrusted with the care and instruction of children, --
usually in their homes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Governing</ent>⟦br⟧
